  "worklog": "## 2026-03-30 05:38 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 1] Copy Signal Following Bot Farms \u2014 Confirmed Root Cause\n\n**Task:** Investigate WHY copy signal hurts WR. Analyze the top wallet database feeding the signal.\n\n**Finding:** **ALL 20 \"top\" wallets in the copy intelligence database are bot farm wallets with $0 earnings.**\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| Wallets with exactly 30 trades | 11 |\n| Wallets with exactly 60 trades | 7 |\n| Wallets with exactly 90 trades | 2 |\n| Wallets with positive earnings | **0** |\n| Biggest loser | \"Warped-Cloak\": -$50,285 |\n\nPerfect multiples of 30 = coordinated bot farm (identified in Mar 29 bug fix but wallet list never refreshed). The copy intelligence pipeline is: bot farm wallets \u2192 copy-signals.json \u2192 live-signals.json \u2192 conviction boost in trading_bot.py \u2192 WORSE WR.\n\nCurrent live signal: 88% bearish confidence based on 47/50 down signals from these bot wallets. This is noise, not alpha.\n\n**Signal chain audit:**\n- `pm-copy-scanner.py` (30 min cron) \u2192 produces bot-farm-polluted wallet list\n- `copy_scanner_v2.py` (5 min cron) \u2192 order flow data (fresh but from bad wallets)\n- `copy-signal-integrator.py` (30 min cron) \u2192 combines into live-signals.json\n- `trading_bot.py` reads live-signals.json \u2192 +1 conviction boost when \"confident\"\n\n**My thinking:** The copy signal was designed to reverse-engineer profitable traders. Instead it found bot farms (high activity = high score, no profit tracking). The Mar 29 bug fixes (Up/Down matching, bot farm filter, SELL-side) were applied to the integrator but the upstream wallet scanner was never updated. We need to either:\n- (a) Rebuild the scanner with profit tracking + bot farm filter\n- (b) Disable the entire copy pipeline and rely on our 4 core indicators (77% WR without copy)\n\nOption (b) is correct for now. Our core indicators work. Copy is broken. Fix it later when we have a proper profit-tracking scanner.\n\n**Decision:**\n1. V4 will set `copy_conviction_boost = 0` (CONFIRMED \u2014 this is the #1 priority V4 change)\n2. Copy crons remain running (cheap, data may be useful for future analysis)\n3. Future: rebuild pm-wallet-scanner.py with outcome tracking (needs PM resolution API)\n\n**Next P1 heartbeat:** After V4 deploys with copy disabled, track WR of first 30 trades as baseline. If WR \u2265 65%, copy stays disabled permanently.\n\n## 2026-03-30 05:08 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 4] Fear & Greed Module Built + Bot Stability Confirmed\n\n**Task:** Wire F&G signal into bot confidence scoring (HEARTBEAT.md P4 task). Confirm bot stability after infra fix.\n\n**Finding:**\n1. **Built `src/fear_greed.py`** \u2014 production-ready module with:\n   - `get_fear_greed()` \u2192 fetches current F&G with 1h cache\n   - `fg_confidence_modifier(value)` \u2192 edge adjustment (-0.10 to +0.10)\n   - `fg_position_multiplier(value)` \u2192 size scaling (0.50x to 1.25x)\n   - Tested: F&G=8 \u2192 +0.10 edge boost, 1.25x position size\n\n2. **V4 integration plan written** (`patches/v4-fear-greed.patch.md`):\n   - 6 exact code insertion points in trading_bot.py\n   - Edge ",
